    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303180/extras/3ab01c3fc7f07d67b9c9cbe452ce657b.avif?t=1753368933\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303180/extras_big/3ab01c3fc7f07d67b9c9cbe452ce657b.avif?t=1753368933 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一款令人着迷的<i><strong>动作类 Roguelike 游戏</strong></i>，在无尽的敌人浪潮中奋战！在《甜蜜屠戮》中，选择一个拥有独特<strong>技能</strong>的英雄，与越来越多的怪物战斗。每次升级后，你可以从<strong>强化和增益</strong>中进行选择，提升你的属性并获得额外的<strong>特殊效果</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 15 分钟后，一个强大的<strong>Boss</strong> 会出现，你必须击败它才能成功完成冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303180/extras/9cd2587df34f2abe43b1817dab222189.poster.avif?t=1753368933\" width=800 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303180/extras/9cd2587df34f2abe43b1817dab222189.webm?t=1753368933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303180/extras/9cd2587df34f2abe43b1817dab222189.mp4?t=1753368933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的英雄</strong>：从各种角色中选择，每位角色都拥有独特的<strong>技能</strong>和玩法风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略选择</strong>：选择你的<strong>属性强化</strong>，解锁强大的<strong>效果增益</strong>，在战斗中获得独特优势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存模式</strong>：你能在怪物的浪潮中存活 15 分钟吗？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好接受挑战，测试你的<strong>技能</strong>和战略决策，与可爱但致命的怪物战斗吧！</p>",
